is to make peace in here, right?

05:29.220 --> 05:31.310
Sing <i>It's a Small World</i>
or whatever the fuck that is.

05:31.510 --> 05:33.310
What happens when I'm out?
What you want me to do then?

05:33.510 --> 05:35.700
Hold everybody hand
and sing <i>Kumbaya</i> and shit?

05:47.310 --> 05:50.280
[train whistle]

05:52.920 --> 05:54.250
[Mike frustrated exhaling]

05:57.420 --> 05:59.710
Want you to keep your eyes
and ears on Davidson.

05:59.910 --> 06:02.510
Any of those AB COs
making any moves,

06:02.710 --> 06:03.760
can you let me know?

06:04.330 --> 06:07.060
He's already told the guards
to loosen the grip, so...

06:08.500 --> 06:10.400
Good. You good?

06:11.230 --> 06:12.400
Peachy.

06:14.940 --> 06:17.770
Hey, Carney, I gotta ask

06:18.070 --> 06:20.190
if you're rolling
with these AB COs.

06:20.390 --> 06:21.330
What?

06:21.530 --> 06:23.280
- Gotta ask.
- I mean, fuck, no.

06:23.980 --> 06:25.060
Come on, Mike, you know me.

06:25.260 --> 06:27.200
You know I'm
an equal opportunity asshole.

06:27.400 --> 06:29.670
I hate them all. AB, COs,

06:29.870 --> 06:31.200
white, black, brown,
fucking yellow,

06:31.400 --> 06:34.290
they're all steaming piles
of useless shit in this joint.

06:34.660 --> 06:35.810
Yeah. Okay.

06:36.010 --> 06:38.330
Look, until this clears up,
I need a favor.

06:38.930 --> 06:43.500
[theme music]

07:51.200 --> 07:52.350
Oh, fuck.

07:52.550 --> 07:53.550
What's up, motherfuckers?

07:53.750 --> 07:56.300
Can I know
who the fuck you are? Huh?

07:57.310 --> 07:59.070
Oh, Jesus Christ.

08:06.720 --> 08:07.900
You motherfuckers lost?

08:08.100 --> 08:09.070
Who the fuck are you?

08:09.270 --> 08:10.400
Don't you fucking worry
about it.

08:10.600 --> 08:12.970
Hey, hey, hey, no, no, no.
We don't need this.

08:13.170 --> 08:16.370
Relax. All right?
Fucking relax! Stop!

08:16.580 --> 08:18.740
Nobody fucking wants this,
including me!

08:18.940 --> 08:20.080
Get your Opie asses
out of here.

08:20.280 --> 08:22.150
Hey, hey, let's fucking
get our shit down.

08:22.350 --> 08:25.370
Right, hey, where the fuck
are you, first of all?

08:26.200 --> 08:28.120
Maybe they're a little lost,
confused.

08:28.320 --> 08:30.190
Maybe you're fucking confused,
right?

08:30.390 --> 08:33.380
Didn't get the memo that there's
order on the streets again.

08:34.540 --> 08:36.060
We sling our own blocks.

08:36.260 --> 08:37.700
Like we used to, right?

08:37.900 --> 08:39.200
You sling here, you die here.

08:39.400 --> 08:42.180
Yes, we do,
so fuck off to your block.

08:42.450 --> 08:43.950
Be fucking smart.

08:45.820 --> 08:46.910
The fuck outta here.

08:47.110 --> 08:49.020
[Mike] Sling in
a fucking sea of blue.

08:49.320 --> 08:50.530
Dipshits.

08:52.560 --> 08:55.430
[Man] They lucky your ass came
in when you did, bro.

08:57.170 --> 08:58.200
Yeah.

09:00.440 --> 09:01.990
All right, everything else
all right

09:02.190 --> 09:03.790
outside these fucking clowns?

09:03.990 --> 09:05.340
Yeah, bro.

09:05.710 --> 09:06.860
And fucking Rhonda says

09:07.060 --> 09:08.980
you need to come by,
check on her sometime.

09:10.650 --> 09:13.220
Yeah. Yeah, sure.

09:14.280 --> 09:16.570
Best be careful where you put
that marshmallow topping, bro.

09:16.770 --> 09:18.000
Shit get messy real fast,

09:18.200 --> 09:19.810
you start playing
with fam', fam'.

09:20.010 --> 09:20.870
I'm just saying.

09:21.070 --> 09:22.410
[Mike] Don't you worry about it.

09:22.610 --> 09:24.030
I ain't worried.

09:25.390 --> 09:26.560
Fuck.

09:42.410 --> 09:44.130
[music]

09:44.330 --> 09:47.900
[siren wailing]

09:48.100 --> 09:49.180
[phone ringing]

09:50.490 --> 09:52.710
[murmured chatter]

09:52.910 --> 09:54.490
Kyle.

09:55.260 --> 09:57.660
Yeah. Yeah, hey, Cap.

09:58.430 --> 09:59.380
How are you holding up?

09:59.580 --> 10:00.950
- Yeah, I'm good.
- Uh-huh?

10:01.150 --> 10:02.310
Um, you seen Ian?

10:02.510 --> 10:03.730
I'm looking for him too.

10:04.670 --> 10:06.280
You're next up with IA,
you know that?

10:06.480 --> 10:07.970
Yeah. Yeah.

10:08.740 --> 10:12.010
Yeah, you, you fellas
got your stories straight?

10:14.110 --> 10:16.540
Well, um,

10:17.680 --> 10:19.460
we were the victims, Cap.

10:19.660 --> 10:21.100
They were fucking crazy
in there,

10:21.300 --> 10:23.500
the inmates killing,
and they were shooting at us.

10:23.700 --> 10:25.790
- [Captain Heard] Yeah.
- Fucking raping COs.

10:26.320 --> 10:28.990
So tell me how the fuck
are we on trial for this?

10:29.260 --> 10:30.890
You're not, son.

10:32.630 --> 10:34.900
Robert and his guys are heroes.

10:36.300 --> 10:37.930
You know how this goes.

10:38.670 --> 10:41.040
Protests, politics, bullshit.

10:41.900 --> 10:44.220
It's all dog and pony show
for the money folks

10:44.420 --> 10:47.790
and the suits and the papers
and the 24-hour news cycle.

10:47.990 --> 10:50.000
- And you're a good-looking kid.
- Mm.

10:50.200 --> 10:51.730
Just a matter of time
before they hit you up

10:51.930 --> 10:54.230
to do Anderson Cooper
or fucking Hannity or whoever.

10:54.430 --> 10:55.370
Robert was doing his job.

10:55.570 --> 10:57.100
All his men were doing
their jobs.

10:57.300 --> 10:59.550
They saved their fucking lives.
End of story.

11:01.390 --> 11:03.230
They want a body, Kyle.

11:03.660 --> 11:05.340
They need someone
to let them know

11:05.540 --> 11:06.610
that the world makes sense,

11:06.810 --> 11:09.260
that there's a crime
and there's a punishment.

11:10.800 --> 11:12.120
If there is no bad guy,

11:12.320 --> 11:15.770
how the fuck do we get to keep
being the good guys, huh?

11:36.160 --> 11:37.690
[Raphael] One little strike
though.

11:38.060 --> 11:39.640
We just keep doing
what the fuck we doing.

11:39.850 --> 11:40.980
The fuck you lookin' at?

11:41.180 --> 11:42.550
We got something for him,
don't worry about it.

11:42.750 --> 11:44.120
[Raphael] Yeah...

11:44.320 --> 11:45.730
- He's scared.
- Yeah, I know.

11:46.200 --> 11:47.990
- What's up, big homie?
- [Man] Good to see ya.

11:48.190 --> 11:49.740
How ya doin'?

11:50.770 --> 11:53.010
[Woman's voice
over PA]

11:54.240 --> 11:56.850
[music]

11:58.110 --> 12:01.150
[inmate chatter]

12:05.120 --> 12:10.210
[music]

12:10.410 --> 12:11.540
Hey, what the fuck is this, man?

12:11.740 --> 12:13.050
[Carney] Hey, pinhead.

12:13.250 --> 12:15.300
