and get back to your cell.

12:16.060 --> 12:17.130
Now.

12:19.940 --> 12:21.970
- Let's go.
- They fucking tossed it.

12:22.770 --> 12:25.210
Are you hard of hearing?
Let's go.

12:27.040 --> 12:29.080
Ever get tired
of this shit, bruh?

12:30.280 --> 12:34.180
