12:39.020 --> 12:41.160
Made them extra large
for you, Bunny.

12:41.990 --> 12:44.160
All right, let's go.
Start hoppin'.

12:45.130 --> 12:46.290
Take it down.

12:57.510 --> 12:59.770
Keep moving,
all the way to the end.

13:01.610 --> 13:03.280
Fuck is this, man?

13:09.920 --> 13:11.070
The fuck you doing, Carney?

13:11.270 --> 13:13.790
Right up against the wall,
wait right there.

13:18.090 --> 13:22.870
[music]

13:34.110 --> 13:35.240
Home sweet home.

13:36.380 --> 13:37.630
[Raphael] Oh, shit.

13:37.830 --> 13:39.750
