pasta sauce and shit,

13:48.410 --> 13:49.710
eating lobsters and steaks,

13:49.910 --> 13:51.380
and cutting garlic
with razors...

13:51.580 --> 13:52.710
That was <i>The Godfather.</i>

13:52.910 --> 13:54.710
It was fucking <i>Goodfellas.</i>
I looked it up.

13:54.910 --> 13:56.010
- I don't think so.
- [Carney] Hey, fuck you.

13:56.210 --> 13:57.550
You wanna go back
to your old cell?

13:57.750 --> 13:58.680
How did this shit happen?

13:58.880 --> 14:01.520
The mayor got you an upgrade.

14:01.720 --> 14:03.240
Fuck, yeah, he did.

14:04.240 --> 14:05.840
Yeah.

14:07.580 --> 14:08.980
Okay.

14:10.410 --> 14:13.280
I'll be sure to tell him
how fucking grateful you are.

14:14.780 --> 14:16.420
Enjoy your stay.

14:19.390 --> 14:20.540
It was <i>Goodfellas.</i>

14:20.740 --> 14:22.290
Fuck up outta here.

14:25.530 --> 14:26.900
Yeah.

14:51.650 --> 14:52.970
Hey.

14:53.170 --> 14:55.960
People downstairs said
everyone's off for the week,

14:56.460 --> 14:57.760
except for you.

15:00.630 --> 15:02.160
You don't want
any of this, Mike.

15:03.370 --> 15:06.650
Yeah. It wasn't my call, Evelyn,
obviously...

15:06.850 --> 15:07.820
Fuck you.

15:08.020 --> 15:08.990
[Mike] And I didn't
know the guy.

15:09.190 --> 15:11.170
This should not have happened.

15:13.310 --> 15:14.530
But he asked for it.

15:14.730 --> 15:16.760
Go away. I swear to fucking God,

15:16.960 --> 15:18.460
if you don't get the fuck
out of my office,

15:18.660 --> 15:20.480
I will have you fucking removed.

15:21.750 --> 15:23.640
This is on you, Mike.

15:23.840 --> 15:24.870
His blood is on you.

15:25.070 --> 15:26.450
[Mike] The fuck it is.

15:27.690 --> 15:28.970
This war's what I'm trying
to stop.

15:29.170 --> 15:30.580
It is not stopping, Mike.

15:30.780 --> 15:31.880
How simple are you?

15:32.080 --> 15:34.680
There is no peace.
There will be no peace.

15:34.880 --> 15:39.070
There is no band-aid big enough
to stop this fucking bleeding.

15:41.340 --> 15:43.510
[Mike sighing] Evelyn.

15:44.070 --> 15:46.040
Lockett went back on his word.

15:46.340 --> 15:48.530
He put the target
on his own back.

15:48.730 --> 15:49.860
Do you understand?

15:50.060 --> 15:51.700
And then goes around
puffing his fucking chest

15:51.900 --> 15:53.430
like he's a law-and-order hero,

15:53.630 --> 15:55.070
knowing full well
he's not the law

15:55.270 --> 15:57.070
and that the order
was only temporary.

15:57.270 --> 16:01.120
He knew what he was fucking with
and who he was fucking over.

16:03.190 --> 16:05.180
But that's done now, Evelyn.

16:05.380 --> 16:06.360
Get out.

16:08.500 --> 16:09.900
You have the pen now.

16:12.030 --> 16:13.840
You can turn this around

16:14.440 --> 16:15.840
and be smart.

16:16.470 --> 16:17.460
It can be quiet.

16:17.660 --> 16:18.790
No one has to know it's you.

16:18.990 --> 16:20.340
[Evelyn]Not anymore, Mike.

16:21.040 --> 16:23.580
Quiet is a luxury
for peace time.

16:26.710 --> 16:28.820
We are at war now.

16:30.120 --> 16:33.890
The war only ends
when you sign the treaty.

16:35.220 --> 16:39.460
Okay, this...
This is the treaty.

16:48.440 --> 16:50.490
[rock music]

16:50.690 --> 16:52.970
Hey, Kyle,
Captain talk to you or what?

16:53.910 --> 16:56.490
Yeah. He said we gotta
get our stories straight.

16:56.690 --> 16:58.900
"Story." Singular. Okay?

16:59.100 --> 17:00.730
That's it.
There's only one fucking story.

17:00.930 --> 17:03.120
All right? That's all
you gotta worry about.

17:10.460 --> 17:11.780
[Ian] Lew, how's it going?

17:11.980 --> 17:12.840
[Lewis] Hey, it's going.

17:13.040 --> 17:14.210
[Ian] Let's have a Coors,

17:14.410 --> 17:17.120
and a Jack and Coke, or
whatever, whatever Mikey wants.

17:17.320 --> 17:18.950
- [Lewis] Whiskey, Mikey?
- Yeah.

17:19.150 --> 17:22.670
Uh, hold the Coke, Lew, for me.

17:24.510 --> 17:26.040
Good man, thank you.

17:26.970 --> 17:28.630
Robert and his team
saved our fucking lives.

17:28.830 --> 17:30.760
Yeah, I know that. I know that.

17:30.960 --> 17:32.260
It's just the Captain,
he wants us

17:32.460 --> 17:33.930
to, you know, talk
about the details.

17:34.130 --> 17:35.470
Gotta sync the details.

17:35.670 --> 17:36.930
That's the shit
that's gonna trip us up.

17:37.140 --> 17:38.040
No fucking tripping us up.

17:38.240 --> 17:39.800
I mean, we're in
the goddamn right, period.

17:40.000 --> 17:41.860
That's it. End of story.

17:44.530 --> 17:45.710
- What's up?
- [Ian] Hey, man.

17:45.910 --> 17:47.380
- [Mike] What do you wanna order?
- [Robert] Hey, Lew.

17:47.580 --> 17:48.750
Can I get a beer?

17:48.950 --> 17:50.420
Actually, fuck that,
just a shot.

17:50.620 --> 17:51.980
I don't have time for beer.

17:52.180 --> 17:53.050
Whatever, it doesn't matter.

17:53.250 --> 17:54.700
Yeah.

17:55.000 --> 17:56.150
I found the rat.

17:56.350 --> 17:58.260
What? You're kidding me?

17:58.460 --> 18:00.660
Yeah, I fucking found him.

18:00.860 --> 18:01.530
Who is it?

18:01.730 --> 18:03.200
It's fucking Ben Morrisey.

18:03.400 --> 18:04.600
[Kyle] Jesus fuck!

18:04.800 --> 18:06.230
That motherfucker.
He was in it with us.

18:06.430 --> 18:07.330
- [Robert] Yeah.
- Probably took out

18:07.530 --> 18:08.950
20 guys himself.

18:09.620 --> 18:11.070
- You talk to him?
- No, not yet.

18:11.270 --> 18:12.900
I mean, my lawyer said
that I fucking shouldn't,

18:13.100 --> 18:14.110
but I don't know.

18:14.310 --> 18:16.740
Your lawyer's fucking right.
Don't talk to him.

18:16.940 --> 18:18.030
Yeah.

18:18.460 --> 18:19.410
Mike, you want me to go?

18:19.610 --> 18:22.330
No. You neither, Kyle.

18:22.730 --> 18:24.620
Nobody fucking talk to this guy.
I'll do it.

18:24.820 --> 18:26.980
I don't like it, Mike.
I don't fucking like it.

18:27.190 --> 18:28.290
We got IA tomorrow.

18:28.490 --> 18:29.640
[knocking on counter]
Lew.

18:31.010 --> 18:31.920
All of you?

18:32.120 --> 18:33.090
No, I already did mine.

18:33.290 --> 18:35.110
Just these two
and a couple guys from the team.

18:37.110 --> 18:38.230
Morrisey?

18:38.430 --> 18:40.060
That fucking guy
already talked to the DA,

18:40.270 --> 18:42.550
so the IA doesn't need him.

18:43.850 --> 18:46.190
All right, well, he's still
